caption: Perfect warm weather people watching spot. When it's warm and they open the windows, sitting at the window looking out on Patricia's Green, enjoying a cold beverage is a fantastic way to enjoy a summerish day. Note I didn't actually say summer. The warmest times in SF are the spring and fall.

On a Wednesday afternoon, my visiting girlfriend and I had a great time with the locals, including a sweet man and his pet cockatoo bird Ghost, who hung out at the open window when sunny. Very friendly bartender and people.
